FBIS3-28890 "dreas030_c_94029" FBIS-EAS-94-030 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Feb 1994 North Korea Foreign Minister Greets Venezuelan Counterpart SK1102013994 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1503 GMT 10 Feb 94 SK1102013994 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, February 10 (KCNA) -- Foreign Minister Kim Yong-nam sent a message of greetings to Miguel Angel Burelli Rivas upon his appointment as foreign minister of the Republic of Venezuela. Expressing the belief that the friendly relations between the two countries would continue developing favourably, the message wished him success at his new post.
